_:B6247d20b813c703a10fe9085341ee0f9 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Smooth Muscle Contraction" <https://purl.wholepersonphysiome.org/wpp/muscular-system> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0006939> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> <https://purl.wholepersonphysiome.org/wpp/muscular-system> .
