<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0000978> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "The portion of the hindlimb that contains both the stylopod and zeugopod." <https://purl.wholepersonphysiome.org/wpp/muscular-system> .
