<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0001630> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Organ consisting of a tissue made up of various elongated cells that are specialized to contract and thus to produce movement and mechanical work[GO]." <https://purl.wholepersonphysiome.org/wpp/muscular-system> .
